【Sturdy & Durable】Nightstand is constructed of high-quality MDF Board and metal legs. Overall dimension:11.42"D x 15.35"W x 22.02"H . The bottom anti-slip rubber pads can prevent the floor from scratches and reduce noises when being moved.. This minimalist headboard is very easy to assemble, with all the accessories and instructions included, and takes a few minutes to install easily.

【Multi-scenario Use】This practical chest of drawers is both beautiful and practical, With a height to match most beds, sofas and chairs, its sleek, minimalist design is also suitable for a variety of settings, it can be used not only as a side table in the bedroom but also as an end table in the living room.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This was the cheapest of several similar options. Don’t expect super high quality but that’s to be expected with the price. The drawer did have a small chip but I didn’t mind that too much. Instructions were clear until they were incorrect for two steps so had to common sense it. Picture getting to the end and getting extremely frustrated the drawer wasn’t working (put the drawer nails in equal places on both sliders as opposed to what the diagram says).All in all, good for small space and offers some storage and display, just don’t expect high quality and you won’t be disappointed
